    "description": "KROMATICUBE is a simple arcade game where you have to avoid obstacles while listenning to chiptune musics.  Stay alive for at least 60 seconds to complete a level. It is designed for tryharder gamers and all retro gaming lovers.<br><br>Each level has it own chiptune music and ramdomly generated obstacles.<br><br>-----<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features List</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>    6 different levels with their own atmosphere<br></li><li>    25 different patterns and obstacles <br></li><li>    Infinite scoring possible</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1753440/extras/03abc180ad916c6f8016dc51b7d74733.poster.avif?t=1735310591\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1753440/extras/03abc180ad916c6f8016dc51b7d74733.webm?t=1735310591\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1753440/extras/03abc180ad916c6f8016dc51b7d74733.mp4?t=1735310591\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Addictive</h2>Technically you can finish the game in only 6 minutes BUT you need to practice a lot before reaching a satisfying level of skills and reflexes. Kromaticube is an alchemy between music and obstacles. A great person said <i>&quot;Just because you fail once, doesn’t mean you’re gonna fail at everything&quot;</i>, and this is the point Kromaticube.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1753440/extras/bfe8332191be54fad66ab3002f2fcf87.poster.avif?t=1735310591\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1753440/extras/bfe8332191be54fad66ab3002f2fcf87.webm?t=1735310591\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1753440/extras/bfe8332191be54fad66ab3002f2fcf87.mp4?t=1735310591\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Satisfying</h2>Kromaticube is a really good game for training your brain reflexes. It's all about learning patterns while discovering new atmospheres. Each level is about one ne particular feeling like joy, sadness or fear for example.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1753440/extras/28eca782fef4d343f27e8e839a7e8fc3.poster.avif?t=1735310591\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1753440/extras/28eca782fef4d343f27e8e839a7e8fc3.webm?t=1735310591\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1753440/extras/28eca782fef4d343f27e8e839a7e8fc3.mp4?t=1735310591\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
